               <p>Mrs. WATTS sworn. - My husband is a <rs id="t18020918-90-viclabel481" type="occupation">hairdresser</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18020918-90-victim665 t18020918-90-viclabel481"></join>, and lives in <placeName id="t18020918-90-crimeloc482">Church-street, Mile-end</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18020918-90-crimeloc482" type="placeName" value="Church-street, Mile-end"></interp>
